[32m+[m[32m## 📱 Responsive Breakpoints[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Mobile**: < şu pso[m
[32m+[m[32mlterrum[m[41m [m
[32m+[m[32m- **Tablet**: 768px - 1024px[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Desktop**: > 1024px[m
